Job Summary</p>
<p>
Blue Box is looking for a tech-savvy sales person with a talent for business development who is excited about playing a pivotal role in the growth and success of our organization. We are looking for someone with the ability to drive the sales cycle from start to finish: cold calls, building pipelines, and closing business. This person will have a consultative sales approach, a drive to develop client relationships and understand client needs, and the ability to communicate how our hosted solutions can help.</p>
<p>
We&#39;re growing fast, and you have a chance to get in on the ground floor. If you&rsquo;re looking for an exciting sales opportunity that combines the sustainability of a company that&rsquo;s been around since 2003 with the excitement of a start-up, join us!</p>
