			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Blue Box is a managed hosting company that is growing fast. If you&rsquo;re looking for an exciting sales position and a way to gain experience in the technology industry, combining the sustainability of a company that&rsquo;s been around since 2003 with the excitement of a start-up, Blue Box is for you.</p>
<p>
The Outbound Lead Generator is primarily a communications position and requires outbound telephone-prospecting functions to our targeted prospects. The Outbound Lead Generator will utilize professional communication, research and interviewing skills, as well as marketing and sales skills.&nbsp; This individual will work closely with our Director of Sales and our Sales Team.&nbsp; If the ability to see your impact on a daily basis is something that you&rsquo;re interested in, then join us!</p>
<p>
<strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Conduct outbound calls into companies across the US and speak to prospective clients about their business needs and initiatives.</li>
<li>
Identify who the most appropriate decision maker is in the company by speaking with multiple company representatives as described above.</li>
<li>
Initiate a conversation with the decision maker to introduce our products &amp; services</li>
<li>
Educate the decision maker on the value Blue Box Group can offer our prospects and then determine if the company would be a good fit for our Sales Executives to sell to.</li>
<li>
Once a sales-ready lead is identified, pass the lead to our Sales Executives for further qualification and follow up.</li>
<li>
Utilize phone and email to communicate with the companies that are assigned via Salesforce.com.</li>
<li>
Update SalesForce.com after each contact with prospective clients with clear and concise notes.</li>
</ul>
